    <equation labels="LABEL:eq:1:1:1" xml:id="S0.E5">
      <tags>
        <tag>(5)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">5</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="H(\mu)=H(\mu_{0})+[D{\tilde{}}H]({\tilde{}}X_{0})\cdot({\tilde{}}X-{\tilde{}}X%&#10;_{0})+o(\|{\tilde{}}X-{\tilde{}}X_{0}\|_{2})" text="H * mu = H * mu _ 0 + (delimited-[]@(D * tilde@(absent) * H) * tilde@(absent) * X _ 0) cdot (tilde@(absent) * X - tilde@(absent) * X _ 0) + o * (norm@(tilde@(absent) * X - tilde@(absent) * X _ 0)) _ 2" xml:id="S0.E5.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMApp>
            <XMTok meaning="equals" role="RELOP">=</XMTok>
            <XMApp>
              <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
              <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">H</XMTok>
              <XMDual>
                <XMRef idref="S0.E5.m1.1"/>

    <equation labels="LABEL:fo:Lip" xml:id="S0.E7">
      <tags>
        <tag>(7)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">7</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|\partial u({\mathbb{P}}_{X})(X)-\partial u({\mathbb{P}}_{%&#10;Y})(Y)|^{2}\bigr{]}\leq C^{2}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|X-Y|^{2}\bigr{]}," text="E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@(partial-differential@(u) * P _ X * X - partial-differential@(u) * P _ Y * Y)) ^ 2) less= C ^ 2 * E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@(X - Y)) ^ 2)" xml:id="S0.E7.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.E7.m1.3"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.E7.m1.3">
                <XMTok meaning="less-than-or-equals" name="leq" role="RELOP">≤</XMTok>
<!--  %**** String Line 100 **** -->                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                  <XMTok font="blackboard" role="UNKNOWN">E</XMTok>
                  <XMDual>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="delimited-[]"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E7.m1.3.1"/>
                    </XMApp>
                    <XMWrap>
                      <XMTok fontsize="120%" role="OPEN" stretchy="false">[</XMTok>
                      <XMApp xml:id="S0.E7.m1.3.1">
                        <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                        <XMDual>
                          <XMApp>
                            <XMTok meaning="absolute-value"/>
                            <XMRef idref="S0.E7.m1.3.1.1"/>
                          </XMApp>
                          <XMWrap>
                            <XMTok role="VERTBAR" stretchy="false">|</XMTok>
                            <XMApp xml:id="S0.E7.m1.3.1.1">
                              <XMTok meaning="minus" role="ADDOP">-</XMTok>
                              <XMApp>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex14">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\inf_{X,{\mathbb{P}}_{X}=\mu}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|\partial u(\mu)(X)-\partial u%&#10;(\nu)(X)|^{2}\bigr{]}\leq 4C^{2}W_{2}({\mathbb{P}}_{X},{\mathbb{P}}_{Y})^{2}" text="(infimum _ (list@(X, P _ X) = mu))@(E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@(partial-differential@(u) * mu * X - partial-differential@(u) * nu * X)) ^ 2)) less= 4 * C ^ 2 * W _ 2 * (open-interval@(P _ X, P _ Y)) ^ 2" xml:id="S0.Ex14.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMApp>
            <XMTok meaning="less-than-or-equals" name="leq" role="RELOP">≤</XMTok>
            <XMApp>
              <XMApp scriptpos="mid">
                <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="mid2"/>
                <XMTok meaning="infimum" role="LIMITOP" scriptpos="mid">inf</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="equals" role="RELOP">=</XMTok>
                  <XMDual>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="list"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.Ex14.m1.1"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.Ex14.m1.2"/>
                    </XMApp>
                    <XMWrap>
                      <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.Ex14.m1.1">X</XMTok>
                      <XMTok fontsize="70%" role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>
                      <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex14.m1.2">
                        <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post3"/>
                        <XMTok font="blackboard" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">P</XMTok>
                        <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="50%" role="UNKNOWN">X</XMTok>
                      </XMApp>
                    </XMWrap>
                  </XMDual>
                  <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" name="mu" role="UNKNOWN">μ</XMTok>
                </XMApp>
              </XMApp>
              <XMApp>
                <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                <XMTok font="blackboard" role="UNKNOWN">E</XMTok>
                <XMDual>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="delimited-[]"/>
                    <XMRef idref="S0.Ex14.m1.7"/>

                    <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex14.m1.7">
                      <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                      <XMDual>
                        <XMApp>
                          <XMTok meaning="absolute-value"/>
                          <XMRef idref="S0.Ex14.m1.7.1"/>

                          <XMTok role="VERTBAR" stretchy="false">|</XMTok>

                            <XMTok meaning="minus" role="ADDOP">-</XMTok>
                            <XMApp>
                              <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>

  <para xml:id="p25">
    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex16">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle\partial\bar{u}^{N}({\underline{}}x)\cdot({%&#10;\underline{}}y-{\underline{}}x)&amp;\displaystyle=\sum_{i=1}^{N}\partial_{x_{i}}%&#10;\bar{u}^{N}({\underline{}}x)(y_{i}-x_{i})\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}\partial u(\bar{\mu}^{N})(x_{i})(y_{i}%&#10;-x_{i})\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}\partial u(\mu)(x_{i})(y_{i}-x_{i})+%&#10;\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}[\partial u(\bar{\mu}^{N})(x_{i})-\partial u(\mu)(x_{%&#10;i})](y_{i}-x_{i}).\end{split}" text="(partial-differential@((bar@(u)) ^ N) * underline@(absent) * x) cdot (underline@(absent) * y - underline@(absent) * x) = ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@((partial-differential _ x _ i)@((bar@(u)) ^ N) * underline@(absent) * x * (y _ i - x _ i)) = (1 / N) * ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@(partial-differential@(u) * (bar@(mu)) ^ N * x _ i * (y _ i - x _ i)) = (1 / N) * ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@(partial-differential@(u) * mu * x _ i * (y _ i - x _ i)) + (1 / N) * ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@(delimited-[]@(partial-differential@(u) * (bar@(mu)) ^ N * x _ i - partial-differential@(u) * mu * x _ i) * (y _ i - x _ i))" xml:id="S0.Ex16.m1">

      <tags>
        <tag>(12)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">12</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="g(\mu^{\prime})-g(\mu)-{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}[\partial_{\mu}g(\mu)({\tilde{}}X%&#10;)\cdot({\tilde{}}{X^{\prime}}-{\tilde{}}X)]\geq 0" text="g * mu ^ prime - g * mu - tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ mu)@(g) * mu * tilde@(absent) * X) cdot (tilde@(absent) * X ^ prime - tilde@(absent) * X)) &gt;= 0" xml:id="S0.E12.m1">

        <tag>(22)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">22</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{cases}&amp;dY_{t}=-\partial_{x}H(t,X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},Y_{t},Z_{t},%&#10;\alpha_{t})dt+Z_{t}dW_{t}\\&#10;&amp;\phantom{?????????????????????????}-{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}[\partial_{\mu}{%&#10;\tilde{}}H(t,{\tilde{}}X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},{\tilde{}}Y_{t},{\tilde{}}Z_%&#10;{t},{\tilde{}}\alpha_{t})(X_{t})]dt\\&#10;&amp;Y_{T}=\partial_{x}g(X_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}})+{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}[%&#10;\partial_{\mu}g({\tilde{}}X_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}})(X_{T})]\end{cases}" text="cases@(absent, d * Y _ t = (- (partial-differential _ x)@(H) * vector@(t, X _ t, P _ X _ t, Y _ t, Z _ t, alpha _ t) * d * t) + Z _ t * d * W _ t, absent, - tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((partial-differential _ mu)@(tilde@(absent) * H) * vector@(t, tilde@(absent) * X _ t, P _ X _ t, tilde@(absent) * Y _ t, tilde@(absent) * Z _ t, tilde@(absent) * alpha _ t) * X _ t) * d * t, absent, Y _ T = (partial-differential _ x)@(g) * open-interval@(X _ T, P _ X _ T) + tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((partial-differential _ mu)@(g) * open-interval@(tilde@(absent) * X _ T, P _ X _ T) * X _ T))" xml:id="S0.E22.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>

    <equation labels="LABEL:fo:adjoint'" xml:id="S0.E23">
      <tags>
        <tag>(23)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">23</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle dY_{t}&amp;\displaystyle=-\bigl{[}\partial_{x}b(t,X_{t}%&#10;,{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},\alpha_{t})\odot Y_{t}+\partial_{x}\sigma(t,X_{t},{%&#10;\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},\alpha_{t})\odot Z_{t}+\partial_{x}f(t,X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_%&#10;{X_{t}},\alpha_{t})\bigr{]}dt\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 250.0pt+Z_{t}dW_{t}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 15.0pt-{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}b(t,{%&#10;\tilde{}}X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},{\tilde{}}\alpha_{t})(X_{t})\odot{\tilde{}%&#10;}Y_{t}+\partial_{\mu}\sigma(t,{\tilde{}}X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},{\tilde{}}%&#10;\alpha_{t})(X_{t})\odot{\tilde{}}Z_{t}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 250.0pt+\partial_{\mu}f(t,{\tilde{}}X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X%&#10;_{t}},{\tilde{}}\alpha_{t})(X_{t})\bigr{]}dt,\end{split}" text="d * Y _ t = ((- delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ x)@(b) * vector@(t, X _ t, P _ X _ t, alpha _ t)) direct-product Y _ t + ((partial-differential _ x)@(sigma) * vector@(t, X _ t, P _ X _ t, alpha _ t)) direct-product Z _ t + (partial-differential _ x)@(f) * vector@(t, X _ t, P _ X _ t, alpha _ t)) * d * t) + Z _ t * d * W _ t) - tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((((partial-differential _ mu)@(b) * vector@(t, tilde@(absent) * X _ t, P _ X _ t, tilde@(absent) * alpha _ t) * X _ t) direct-product tilde@(absent)) * Y _ t + (((partial-differential _ mu)@(sigma) * vector@(t, tilde@(absent) * X _ t, P _ X _ t, tilde@(absent) * alpha _ t) * X _ t) direct-product tilde@(absent)) * Z _ t + (partial-differential _ mu)@(f) * vector@(t, tilde@(absent) * X _ t, P _ X _ t, tilde@(absent) * alpha _ t) * X _ t) * d * t" xml:id="S0.E23.m1">

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex35">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle{\mathbb{E}}{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|\partial%&#10;_{\mu}b(t,{\tilde{}}X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},{\tilde{}}\alpha_{t})(X_{t})%&#10;\odot{\tilde{}}Y_{t}|^{2}\bigr{]}\leq c^{\prime}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|Y_{t}|^{2%&#10;}\bigr{]},\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle{\mathbb{E}}{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|\partial_{\mu}\sigma(%&#10;t,{\tilde{}}X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},{\tilde{}}\alpha_{t})(X_{t})\odot{%&#10;\tilde{}}Z_{t}|^{2}\bigr{]}\leq c^{\prime}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|Z_{t}|^{2}\bigr%&#10;{]},\end{split}" text="formulae@(E * tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@((((partial-differential _ mu)@(b) * vector@(t, tilde@(absent) * X _ t, P _ X _ t, tilde@(absent) * alpha _ t) * X _ t) direct-product tilde@(absent)) * Y _ t)) ^ 2) less= c ^ prime * E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@(Y _ t)) ^ 2), E * tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@((((partial-differential _ mu)@(sigma) * vector@(t, tilde@(absent) * X _ t, P _ X _ t, tilde@(absent) * alpha _ t) * X _ t) direct-product tilde@(absent)) * Z _ t)) ^ 2) less= c ^ prime * E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@(Z _ t)) ^ 2))" xml:id="S0.Ex35.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMDual>
              <XMRef idref="S0.Ex35.m1.91"/>
              <XMWrap>
                <XMDual xml:id="S0.Ex35.m1.91">
                  <XMApp>

                  </XMApp>
                  <XMWrap>

                        <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>

                            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex35.m1.4"/>

    <equation labels="LABEL:fo:deltaoft" xml:id="S0.E25">
      <tags>
        <tag>(25)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">25</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle\delta_{t}={\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{%&#10;\mu}b(t,\theta_{t})({\tilde{}}X_{t})\cdot{\tilde{}}V_{t}\bigr{]}={\tilde{}}{%&#10;\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}b(t,x,{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},\alpha)({\tilde{}}%&#10;X_{t})\cdot{\tilde{}}V_{t}\bigr{]}_{{\footnotesize{\left|\begin{array}[]{l}%&#10;\hskip-6.0pt{x=X_{t}}\atop\hskip-6.0pt{\alpha=\alpha_{t}}\end{array}\right.}}}%&#10;,\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle{\tilde{}}\delta_{t}={\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu%&#10;}\sigma(t,\theta_{t})({\tilde{}}X_{t})\cdot{\tilde{}}V_{t}\big{]}={\tilde{}}{%&#10;\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}\sigma(t,x,{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},\alpha)({%&#10;\tilde{}}X_{t})\cdot{\tilde{}}V_{t}\big{]}_{{\footnotesize{\left|\begin{array}%&#10;[]{l}\hskip-6.0pt{x=X_{t}}\atop\hskip-6.0pt{\alpha=\alpha_{t}}\end{array}%&#10;\right.}}},\end{split}" text="formulae@(delta _ t = tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((((partial-differential _ mu)@(b) * open-interval@(t, theta _ t) * tilde@(absent) * X _ t) cdot tilde@(absent)) * V _ t) = tilde@(absent) * E * (delimited-[]@((((partial-differential _ mu)@(b) * vector@(t, x, P _ X _ t, alpha) * tilde@(absent) * X _ t) cdot tilde@(absent)) * V _ t)) _ [|=xXt=ααt], tilde@(absent) * delta _ t = tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((((partial-differential _ mu)@(sigma) * open-interval@(t, theta _ t) * tilde@(absent) * X _ t) cdot tilde@(absent)) * V _ t) = tilde@(absent) * E * (delimited-[]@((((partial-differential _ mu)@(sigma) * vector@(t, x, P _ X _ t, alpha) * tilde@(absent) * X _ t) cdot tilde@(absent)) * V _ t)) _ [|=xXt=ααt])" xml:id="S0.E25.m1">

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle\frac{1}{\epsilon}\left[b(t,\theta_{t}^{\epsilon})-b%&#10;(t,\theta_{t})\right]&amp;\displaystyle=\int_{0}^{1}\partial_{x}b\bigl{(}t,\theta_%&#10;{t}^{\lambda,\epsilon}\bigr{)}\cdot(V^{\epsilon}_{t}+V_{t})d\lambda+\int_{0}^{%&#10;1}\partial_{\alpha}b\bigl{(}t,\theta_{t}^{\lambda,\epsilon}\bigr{)}\cdot\beta_%&#10;{t}d\lambda\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 15.0pt+\int_{0}^{1}{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial%&#10;_{\mu}b\bigl{(}t,\theta_{t}^{\lambda,\epsilon}\bigr{)}\bigl{(}{\tilde{}}X_{t}^%&#10;{\lambda,\epsilon}\bigr{)}\cdot({\tilde{}}V^{\epsilon}_{t}+{\tilde{}}V_{t})%&#10;\bigr{]}d\lambda,\end{split}" text="(1 / epsilon) * delimited-[]@(b * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ epsilon) - b * open-interval@(t, theta _ t)) = ((integral _ 0) ^ 1)@((((partial-differential _ x)@(b) * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ (list@(lambda, epsilon)))) cdot ((V ^ epsilon) _ t + V _ t)) * differential-d@(lambda)) + ((integral _ 0) ^ 1)@((((partial-differential _ alpha)@(b) * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ (list@(lambda, epsilon)))) cdot beta _ t) * differential-d@(lambda)) + ((integral _ 0) ^ 1)@(tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ mu)@(b) * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ (list@(lambda, epsilon))) * tilde@(absent) * (X _ t) ^ (list@(lambda, epsilon))) cdot (tilde@(absent) * (V ^ epsilon) _ t + tilde@(absent) * V _ t)) * differential-d@(lambda))" xml:id="S0.Ex39.m1">

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex46">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle\lim_{\epsilon\searrow 0}\frac{1}{\epsilon}{\mathbb%&#10;{E}}\int_{0}^{T}\bigl{[}f\bigl{(}t,\theta_{t}^{\epsilon}\bigr{)}-f(t,\theta_{t%&#10;})\bigr{]}dt\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 15.0pt=\lim_{\epsilon\searrow 0}\frac{1}{\epsilon}{%&#10;\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}\int_{0}^{1}\frac{d}{d\lambda}f(t,\theta^{\lambda,%&#10;\epsilon}_{t})d\lambda dt\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 15.0pt=\lim_{\epsilon\searrow 0}{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}%&#10;\int_{0}^{1}\bigl{[}\partial_{x}f\bigl{(}t,\theta^{\lambda,\epsilon}_{t}\bigr{%&#10;)}\cdot(V^{\epsilon}_{t}+V_{t})\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 50.0pt+{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}f\bigl%&#10;{(}t,\theta_{t}^{\lambda,\epsilon}\bigr{)}({\tilde{}}X_{t}^{\lambda,\epsilon})%&#10;\cdot({\tilde{}}V^{\epsilon}_{t}+{\tilde{}}V_{t})\bigr{]}+\partial_{\alpha}f%&#10;\bigl{(}t,\theta_{t}^{\lambda,\epsilon}\bigr{)}\cdot\beta_{t}\bigr{]}d\lambda&#10;dt%&#10;\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 15.0pt={\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}\bigl{[}\partial_{x}f(t,%&#10;\theta_{t})\cdot V_{t}+{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}f(t,\theta_%&#10;{t})({\tilde{}}X_{t})\cdot{\tilde{}}V_{t}\bigr{]}+\partial_{\alpha}f(t,\theta_%&#10;{t})\cdot\beta_{t}\bigr{]}dt\end{split}" text="(limit _ (epsilon searrow 0))@((1 / epsilon) * E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(delimited-[]@(f * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ epsilon) - f * open-interval@(t, theta _ t)) * differential-d@(t))) = (limit _ (epsilon searrow 0))@((1 / epsilon) * E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(((integral _ 0) ^ 1)@((d / (d * lambda)) * f * open-interval@(t, (theta ^ (list@(lambda, epsilon))) _ t) * differential-d@(lambda) * differential-d@(t)))) = (limit _ (epsilon searrow 0))@(E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(((integral _ 0) ^ 1)@(delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ x)@(f) * open-interval@(t, (theta ^ (list@(lambda, epsilon))) _ t)) cdot ((V ^ epsilon) _ t + V _ t) + tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ mu)@(f) * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ (list@(lambda, epsilon))) * tilde@(absent) * (X _ t) ^ (list@(lambda, epsilon))) cdot (tilde@(absent) * (V ^ epsilon) _ t + tilde@(absent) * V _ t)) + ((partial-differential _ alpha)@(f) * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ (list@(lambda, epsilon)))) cdot beta _ t) * d@(lambda) * d@(t)))) = E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ x)@(f) * open-interval@(t, theta _ t)) cdot V _ t + tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((((partial-differential _ mu)@(f) * open-interval@(t, theta _ t) * tilde@(absent) * X _ t) cdot tilde@(absent)) * V _ t) + ((partial-differential _ alpha)@(f) * open-interval@(t, theta _ t)) cdot beta _ t) * differential-d@(t))" xml:id="S0.Ex46.m1">

  <para xml:id="p78">
    <equation labels="LABEL:fo:Hgateaux" xml:id="S0.E31">
      <tags>
        <tag>(31)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">31</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\frac{d}{d\epsilon}J(\alpha+\epsilon\beta)\big{|}_{\epsilon=0}={\mathbb{E}}%&#10;\left[\int_{0}^{T}\partial_{\alpha}H(t,X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},Y_{t},\alpha%&#10;_{t})\cdot\beta_{t}\right]dt." text="evaluated-at@((d / (d * epsilon)) * J * (alpha + epsilon * beta), epsilon = 0) = E * delimited-[]@(((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(((partial-differential _ alpha)@(H) * vector@(t, X _ t, P _ X _ t, Y _ t, alpha _ t)) cdot beta _ t)) * d * t" xml:id="S0.E31.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.E31.m1.3"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.E31.m1.3">
                <XMTok meaning="equals" role="RELOP">=</XMTok>
                <XMDual>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="evaluated-at"/>
                    <XMRef idref="S0.E31.m1.3.1"/>
                    <XMRef idref="S0.E31.m1.1"/>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                    <XMWrap>
                      <XMApp xml:id="S0.E31.m1.3.1">
                        <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                        <XMApp>
                          <XMTok mathstyle="display" meaning="divide" role="FRACOP"/>
                          <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">d</XMTok>
                          <XMApp>
                            <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                            <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">d</XMTok>
                            <XMTok font="italic" name="epsilon" role="UNKNOWN">ϵ</XMTok>
                          </XMApp>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\forall\alpha\in A,\quad H(t,X_{t},Y_{t},Z_{t},\alpha_{t})\leq H(t,X_{t},Y_{t}%&#10;,Z_{t},\alpha)\qquad a.e.\text{ in }t\in[0,T],\;{\mathbb{P}}-a.s." text="formulae@(formulae@(for-all@(alpha) element-of A, H * vector@(t, X _ t, Y _ t, Z _ t, alpha _ t) less= list@(H * vector@(t, X _ t, Y _ t, Z _ t, alpha), a)), e, [ in ] * t element-of list@(closed-interval@(0, T), P - a), s)" xml:id="S0.E32.m1">

    <equation labels="LABEL:eq:24:1:1" xml:id="S0.E34">
      <tags>
        <tag>(34)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">34</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle J(\alpha)-J(\alpha^{\prime})&amp;\displaystyle={\mathbb%&#10;{E}}\bigl{[}g(X_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}})-g(X^{\prime}_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X^{%&#10;\prime}_{T}})\bigr{]}+{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}\bigl{[}f(t,\theta_{t})-f(t,%&#10;\theta_{t}^{\prime})\bigr{]}dt\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle={\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}g(X_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}})-g(X^{\prime}_%&#10;{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X^{\prime}_{T}})\bigr{]}+{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}\bigl{[}H(t%&#10;,\Theta_{t})-H(t,\Theta_{t}^{\prime})\bigr{]}dt\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\phantom{????????}-{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}\bigl{\{}\bigl{[}b(t,%&#10;\theta_{t})-b(t,\theta_{t}^{\prime})\bigr{]}\cdot Y_{t}+\bigl{[}\sigma(t,%&#10;\theta_{t})-\sigma(t,\theta^{\prime}_{t})]\cdot Z_{t}\bigr{\}}dt\end{split}" text="J * alpha - J * alpha ^ prime = E * delimited-[]@(g * open-interval@(X _ T, P _ X _ T) - g * open-interval@((X ^ prime) _ T, P _ (X ^ prime) _ T)) + E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(delimited-[]@(f * open-interval@(t, theta _ t) - f * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ prime)) * differential-d@(t)) = (E * delimited-[]@(g * open-interval@(X _ T, P _ X _ T) - g * open-interval@((X ^ prime) _ T, P _ (X ^ prime) _ T)) + E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(delimited-[]@(H * open-interval@(t, Theta _ t) - H * open-interval@(t, (Theta _ t) ^ prime)) * differential-d@(t))) - E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(set@(delimited-[]@(b * open-interval@(t, theta _ t) - b * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ prime)) cdot Y _ t + delimited-[]@(sigma * open-interval@(t, theta _ t) - sigma * open-interval@(t, (theta ^ prime) _ t)) cdot Z _ t) * differential-d@(t))" xml:id="S0.E34.m1">

    <equation labels="LABEL:fo:g" xml:id="S0.E35">
      <tags>
        <tag>(35)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">35</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle{\mathbb{E}}[g(X_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}})-g(X^{%&#10;\prime}_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X^{\prime}_{T}})]\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\leq{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{x}g(X_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}}%&#10;)\cdot(X_{T}-X^{\prime}_{T})+{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}g(X_{%&#10;T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}})({\tilde{}}X_{T})\cdot({\tilde{}}X_{T}-{\tilde{}}{X^{%&#10;\prime}_{T}})\bigr{]}\bigr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle={\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\bigl{(}\partial_{x}g(X_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X%&#10;_{T}})+{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}[\partial_{\mu}g({\tilde{}}X_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_%&#10;{T}})(X_{T})]\bigr{)}\cdot(X_{T}-X^{\prime}_{T})\bigr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle={\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}Y_{T}\cdot(X_{T}-X^{\prime}_{T})\bigr{]}={%&#10;\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}(X_{T}-X^{\prime}_{T})\cdot Y_{T}\bigr{]},\end{split}" text="E * delimited-[]@(g * open-interval@(X _ T, P _ X _ T) - g * open-interval@((X ^ prime) _ T, P _ (X ^ prime) _ T)) less= E * delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ x)@(g) * open-interval@(X _ T, P _ X _ T)) cdot (X _ T - (X ^ prime) _ T) + tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ mu)@(g) * open-interval@(X _ T, P _ X _ T) * tilde@(absent) * X _ T) cdot (tilde@(absent) * X _ T - tilde@(absent) * (X ^ prime) _ T))) = E * delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ x)@(g) * open-interval@(X _ T, P _ X _ T) + tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((partial-differential _ mu)@(g) * open-interval@(tilde@(absent) * X _ T, P _ X _ T) * X _ T)) cdot (X _ T - (X ^ prime) _ T)) = E * delimited-[]@(Y _ T cdot (X _ T - (X ^ prime) _ T)) = E * delimited-[]@((X _ T - (X ^ prime) _ T) cdot Y _ T)" xml:id="S0.E35.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMDual>
              <XMRef idref="S0.E35.m1.152"/>
              <XMWrap>

                  <XMTok meaning="multirelation"/>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}(X_{T}-X^{\prime}_{T})\cdot Y_{%&#10;T}\bigr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle={\mathbb{E}}\biggl{[}\int_{0}^{T}(X_{t}-X^{\prime}_{t})\cdot dY%&#10;_{t}+\int_{0}^{T}Y_{t}\cdot d[X_{t}-X^{\prime}_{t}]+\int_{0}^{T}[\sigma(t,%&#10;\theta_{t})-\sigma(t,\theta_{t}^{\prime})]\cdot Z_{t}dt\biggr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=-{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}\bigl{[}\partial_{x}H(t,\Theta_{t})%&#10;\cdot(X_{t}-X^{\prime}_{t})+{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}H(t,{%&#10;\tilde{}}\Theta_{t})(X_{t})\bigr{]}\cdot(X_{t}-X^{\prime}_{t})\bigr{]}dt\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\phantom{??????}+{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}\bigl{[}[b(t,\theta_{t}%&#10;)-b(t,\theta^{\prime}_{t})]\cdot Y_{t}+[\sigma(t,\theta_{t})-\sigma(t,\theta^{%&#10;\prime}_{t})]\cdot Z_{t}\bigr{]}dt,\end{split}" text="E * delimited-[]@((X _ T - (X ^ prime) _ T) cdot Y _ T) = E * delimited-[]@(((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((X _ t - (X ^ prime) _ t) cdot differential-d@(Y _ t)) + ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((Y _ t cdot d) * delimited-[]@(X _ t - (X ^ prime) _ t)) + ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((delimited-[]@(sigma * open-interval@(t, theta _ t) - sigma * open-interval@(t, (theta _ t) ^ prime)) cdot Z _ t) * differential-d@(t))) = (- E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ x)@(H) * open-interval@(t, Theta _ t)) cdot (X _ t - (X ^ prime) _ t) + (tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((partial-differential _ mu)@(H) * open-interval@(t, tilde@(absent) * Theta _ t) * X _ t)) cdot (X _ t - (X ^ prime) _ t)) * differential-d@(t))) + E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@(delimited-[]@(delimited-[]@(b * open-interval@(t, theta _ t) - b * open-interval@(t, (theta ^ prime) _ t)) cdot Y _ t + delimited-[]@(sigma * open-interval@(t, theta _ t) - sigma * open-interval@(t, (theta ^ prime) _ t)) cdot Z _ t) * differential-d@(t))" xml:id="S0.Ex59.m1">

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex75">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|\partial_{\mu}f(t,x^{\prime},%&#10;\mu^{\prime},\alpha^{\prime})(X^{\prime})-\partial_{\mu}f(t,x,\mu,\alpha)(X)|^%&#10;{2}\bigr{]}\leq\hat{c}\bigl{(}|(x^{\prime},\alpha^{\prime})-(x,\alpha)|^{2}+{%&#10;\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|X^{\prime}-X|^{2}\bigr{]}\bigr{)},\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|\partial_{\mu}g(x^{\prime},\mu^{\prime})(X^%&#10;{\prime})-\partial_{\mu}g(x,\mu)(X)|^{2}\bigr{]}\leq\hat{c}\bigl{(}|x^{\prime}%&#10;-x|^{2}+{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|X^{\prime}-X|^{2}\bigr{]}\bigr{)}.\end{split}" text="formulae@(E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@((partial-differential _ mu)@(f) * vector@(t, x ^ prime, mu ^ prime, alpha ^ prime) * X ^ prime - (partial-differential _ mu)@(f) * vector@(t, x, mu, alpha) * X)) ^ 2) less= hat@(c) * ((absolute-value@(open-interval@(x ^ prime, alpha ^ prime) - open-interval@(x, alpha))) ^ 2 + E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@(X ^ prime - X)) ^ 2)), E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@((partial-differential _ mu)@(g) * open-interval@(x ^ prime, mu ^ prime) * X ^ prime - (partial-differential _ mu)@(g) * open-interval@(x, mu) * X)) ^ 2) less= hat@(c) * ((absolute-value@(x ^ prime - x)) ^ 2 + E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@(X ^ prime - X)) ^ 2)))" xml:id="S0.Ex75.m1">

  <para xml:id="p109">
    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex76">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle f(t,x^{\prime},\mu^{\prime},\alpha^{\prime})-f(t,x%&#10;,\mu,\alpha)\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 15.0pt-\partial_{(x,\alpha)}f(t,x,\mu,\alpha)\cdot(x^{%&#10;\prime}-x,\alpha^{\prime}-\alpha)-\tilde{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}f(t,%&#10;x,\mu,\alpha)({\tilde{}}X)\cdot(\tilde{X}^{\prime}-\tilde{X})\bigr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\geq\lambda|\alpha^{\prime}-\alpha|^{2},\end{split}" text="f * vector@(t, x ^ prime, mu ^ prime, alpha ^ prime) - f * vector@(t, x, mu, alpha) - ((partial-differential _ (open-interval@(x, alpha)))@(f) * vector@(t, x, mu, alpha)) cdot open-interval@(x ^ prime - x, alpha ^ prime - alpha) - tilde@(E) * delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ mu)@(f) * vector@(t, x, mu, alpha) * tilde@(absent) * X) cdot ((tilde@(X)) ^ prime - tilde@(X))) &gt;= lambda * (absolute-value@(alpha ^ prime - alpha)) ^ 2" xml:id="S0.Ex76.m1">

  <para xml:id="p110">
    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex77">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle H(t,x,\mu,y,z,\alpha)&amp;\displaystyle=\bigl{[}b_{0}(t%&#10;)+b_{1}(t)\bar{\mu}+b_{2}(t)x+b_{3}(t)\alpha\bigr{]}\cdot y\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 15.0pt+\bigl{[}\sigma_{0}(t)+\sigma_{1}(t)\bar{\mu}+%&#10;\sigma_{2}(t)x+\sigma_{3}(t)\alpha\bigr{]}\cdot z+f(t,x,\mu,\alpha),\end{split}" text="H * vector@(t, x, mu, y, z, alpha) = delimited-[]@(b _ 0 * t + b _ 1 * t * bar@(mu) + b _ 2 * t * x + b _ 3 * t * alpha) cdot y + delimited-[]@(sigma _ 0 * t + sigma _ 1 * t * bar@(mu) + sigma _ 2 * t * x + sigma _ 3 * t * alpha) cdot z + f * vector@(t, x, mu, alpha)" xml:id="S0.Ex77.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMDual>
              <XMRef idref="S0.Ex77.m1.89"/>
              <XMWrap>
                <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex77.m1.89">
                  <XMRef idref="S0.Ex77.m1.15"/>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                    <XMRef idref="S0.Ex77.m1.1"/>
                    <XMApp>

    <equation labels="LABEL:fo:alphahat" xml:id="S0.E39">
      <tags>
        <tag>(39)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">39</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\hat{\alpha}(t,x,\mu,y,z)=\textrm{argmin}_{\alpha\in{\mathbb{R}}^{k}}H(t,x,\mu%&#10;,y,z,\alpha)." text="hat@(alpha) * vector@(t, x, mu, y, z) = [argmin] _ (alpha element-of R ^ k) * H * vector@(t, x, mu, y, z, alpha)" xml:id="S0.E39.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.E39.m1.12"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.E39.m1.12">
                <XMTok meaning="equals" role="RELOP">=</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok name="hat" role="OVERACCENT" stretchy="false">^</XMTok>
                    <XMTok font="italic" name="alpha" role="UNKNOWN">α</XMTok>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMDual>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="vector"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E39.m1.1"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E39.m1.2"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E39.m1.3"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E39.m1.4"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E39.m1.5"/>
                    </XMApp>
                    <XMWrap>
                      <XMTok role="OPEN" stretchy="false">(</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.E39.m1.1">t</XMTok>
                      <XMTok role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.E39.m1.2">x</XMTok>
                      <XMTok role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" name="mu" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.E39.m1.3">μ</XMTok>
                      <XMTok role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.E39.m1.4">y</XMTok>
                      <XMTok role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.E39.m1.5">z</XMTok>
                      <XMTok role="CLOSE" stretchy="false">)</XMTok>
                    </XMWrap>
                  </XMDual>
                </XMApp>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>

                    <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                    <XMText>argmin</XMText>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="element-of" name="in" role="RELOP">∈</XMTok>

                      <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.E39.m1.6">t</XMTok>
                      <XMTok role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.E39.m1.7">x</XMTok>
                      <XMTok role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>

                      <XMTok role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>

                      <XMTok role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>

                      <XMTok font="italic" name="alpha" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.E39.m1.11">α</XMTok>

                    </XMWrap>
                  </XMDual>
                </XMApp>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{cases}&amp;\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle dX_{t}=\bigl{[}b_{0}(t)+b_{1}(t){%&#10;\mathbb{E}}[X_{t}]+b_{2}(t)X_{t}+b_{3}(t)\hat{\alpha}(t,X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_%&#10;{t}},Y_{t},Z_{t})\bigr{]}dt\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 10.0pt+\bigl{[}\sigma_{0}(t)+\sigma_{1}(t){\mathbb{E}}[X_%&#10;{t}]+\sigma_{2}(t)X_{t}+\sigma_{3}(t)\hat{\alpha}(t,X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}}%&#10;,Y_{t},Z_{t})\bigr{]}dW_{t},\end{split}\\&#10;&amp;\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle dY_{t}=-\bigl{[}\partial_{x}f\bigl{(}t,X_{t},{%&#10;\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},\hat{\alpha}(t,X_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},Y_{t},Z_{t})%&#10;\bigr{)}+b_{2}^{\dagger}(t)Y_{t}+\sigma_{2}^{\dagger}(t)Z_{t}\bigr{]}dt+Z_{t}%&#10;dW_{t}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 10.0pt-\bigl{\{}\tilde{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}f%&#10;\bigl{(}t,\tilde{X}_{t},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},\hat{\alpha}(t,\tilde{X}_{t},{%&#10;\mathbb{P}}_{X_{t}},\tilde{Y}_{t},\tilde{Z}_{t})\bigr{)}(X_{t})\bigr{]}+b_{1}^%&#10;{\dagger}(t){\mathbb{E}}[Y_{t}]+\sigma_{1}^{\dagger}(t){\mathbb{E}}[Z_{t}]%&#10;\bigr{\}}dt,\end{split}\end{cases}" text="cases@(absent, d * X _ t = delimited-[]@(b _ 0 * t + b _ 1 * t * E * delimited-[]@(X _ t) + b _ 2 * t * X _ t + b _ 3 * t * hat@(alpha) * vector@(t, X _ t, P _ X _ t, Y _ t, Z _ t)) * d * t + delimited-[]@(sigma _ 0 * t + sigma _ 1 * t * E * delimited-[]@(X _ t) + sigma _ 2 * t * X _ t + sigma _ 3 * t * hat@(alpha) * vector@(t, X _ t, P _ X _ t, Y _ t, Z _ t)) * d * W _ t, absent, d * Y _ t = ((- delimited-[]@((partial-differential _ x)@(f) * vector@(t, X _ t, P _ X _ t, hat@(alpha) * vector@(t, X _ t, P _ X _ t, Y _ t, Z _ t)) + (b _ 2) ^ dagger * t * Y _ t + (sigma _ 2) ^ dagger * t * Z _ t) * d * t) + Z _ t * d * W _ t) - set@(tilde@(E) * delimited-[]@((partial-differential _ mu)@(f) * vector@(t, (tilde@(X)) _ t, P _ X _ t, hat@(alpha) * vector@(t, (tilde@(X)) _ t, P _ X _ t, (tilde@(Y)) _ t, (tilde@(Z)) _ t)) * X _ t) + (b _ 1) ^ dagger * t * E * delimited-[]@(Y _ t) + (sigma _ 1) ^ dagger * t * E * delimited-[]@(Z _ t)) * d * t)" xml:id="S0.E42.m1">

    <equation labels="LABEL:eq:norm_I" xml:id="S0.E44">

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex81">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\|\Theta-\Theta^{\prime}\|_{\mathbb{S}}\leq C\bigl{(}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|\xi-%&#10;\xi^{\prime}|^{2}\bigr{]}^{1/2}+\|{\mathcal{I}}-{\mathcal{I}}^{\prime}\|_{%&#10;\mathbb{I}}\bigr{)}." text="(norm@(Theta - Theta ^ prime)) _ S less= C * (E * (delimited-[]@((absolute-value@(xi - xi ^ prime)) ^ 2)) ^ (1 / 2) + (norm@(I - I ^ prime)) _ I)" xml:id="S0.Ex81.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex81.m1.1"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex81.m1.1">
                <XMTok meaning="less-than-or-equals" name="leq" role="RELOP">≤</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                  <XMDual>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="norm"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.Ex81.m1.1.1"/>
                    </XMApp>
                    <XMWrap>
                      <XMTok meaning="parallel-to" name="||" role="VERTBAR">∥</XMTok>
                      <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex81.m1.1.1">
                        <XMTok meaning="minus" role="ADDOP">-</XMTok>
                        <XMTok name="Theta" role="UNKNOWN">Θ</XMTok>
                        <XMApp>
                          <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                          <XMTok name="Theta" role="UNKNOWN">Θ</XMTok>
                          <XMTok fontsize="70%" name="prime" role="SUPOP">′</XMTok>
                        </XMApp>
                      </XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="parallel-to" name="||" role="VERTBAR">∥</XMTok>
                    </XMWrap>
                  </XMDual>
                  <XMTok font="blackboard" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">S</XMTok>
                </XMApp>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                  <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">C</XMTok>
                  <XMDual>
                    <XMRef idref="S0.Ex81.m1.1.2"/>
                    <XMWrap>
                      <XMTok fontsize="120%" role="OPEN" stretchy="false">(</XMTok>
                      <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex81.m1.1.2">
                        <XMTok meaning="plus" role="ADDOP">+</XMTok>
                        <XMApp>
                          <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>

                            <XMDual>
                              <XMApp>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}(X_{T}^{\prime}-X_{T})\cdot Y_{T%&#10;}\bigr{]}&amp;\displaystyle=\gamma{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}\bigl{(}\partial_{x}g(X_{T},%&#10;{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}})+{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}[\partial_{\mu}g({\tilde{}}X_{T},{%&#10;\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}})(X_{T})]\bigr{)}\cdot(X_{T}^{\prime}-X_{T})\bigr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 15.0pt+{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}({{\mathcal{I}}^{g,\prime}}_{T%&#10;}-{{\mathcal{I}}^{g}}_{T})\cdot Y_{T}\bigr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\leq\gamma{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}g(X_{T}^{\prime},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{%&#10;T}^{\prime}})-g(X_{T},{\mathbb{P}}_{X_{T}})\bigr{]}+{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}({{%&#10;\mathcal{I}}^{g,\prime}}_{T}-{{\mathcal{I}}^{g}}_{T})\cdot Y_{T}\bigr{]}.\end{split}" text="E * delimited-[]@(((X _ T) ^ prime - X _ T) cdot Y _ T) = gamma * E * delimited-[]@(((partial-differential _ x)@(g) * open-interval@(X _ T, P _ X _ T) + tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@((partial-differential _ mu)@(g) * open-interval@(tilde@(absent) * X _ T, P _ X _ T) * X _ T)) cdot ((X _ T) ^ prime - X _ T)) + E * delimited-[]@(((I ^ (list@(g, prime1))) _ T - (I ^ g) _ T) cdot Y _ T) less= gamma * E * delimited-[]@(g * open-interval@((X _ T) ^ prime, P _ ((X _ T) ^ prime)) - g * open-interval@(X _ T, P _ X _ T)) + E * delimited-[]@(((I ^ (list@(g, prime1))) _ T - (I ^ g) _ T) cdot Y _ T)" xml:id="S0.Ex84.m1">

  <para xml:id="p126">
    <equation labels="LABEL:eq:1:2:3" xml:id="S0.E47">
      <tags>
        <tag>(47)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">47</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\gamma J(\alpha^{\prime})-\gamma J(\alpha)\geq\gamma\lambda{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0%&#10;}^{T}|\alpha_{t}-\alpha_{t}^{\prime}|^{2}dt+T_{0}-T_{2}+{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}({%&#10;{\mathcal{I}}^{g}}_{T}-{{\mathcal{I}}^{g,\prime}}_{T})\cdot Y_{T}\bigr{]}." text="gamma * J * alpha ^ prime - gamma * J * alpha &gt;= ((gamma * lambda * E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((absolute-value@(alpha _ t - (alpha _ t) ^ prime)) ^ 2 * differential-d@(t)) + T _ 0) - T _ 2) + E * delimited-[]@(((I ^ g) _ T - (I ^ (list@(g, prime1))) _ T) cdot Y _ T)" xml:id="S0.E47.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.E47.m1.4"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.E47.m1.4">
                <XMTok meaning="greater-than-or-equals" name="geq" role="RELOP">≥</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="minus" role="ADDOP">-</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                    <XMTok font="italic" name="gamma" role="UNKNOWN">γ</XMTok>
                    <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">J</XMTok>
                    <XMDual>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E47.m1.4.1"/>
                      <XMWrap>
                        <XMTok role="OPEN" stretchy="false">(</XMTok>
                        <XMApp xml:id="S0.E47.m1.4.1">
                          <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                          <XMTok font="italic" name="alpha" role="UNKNOWN">α</XMTok>
                          <XMTok fontsize="70%" name="prime" role="SUPOP">′</XMTok>
                        </XMApp>
                        <XMTok role="CLOSE" stretchy="false">)</XMTok>
                      </XMWrap>
                    </XMDual>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                    <XMTok font="italic" name="gamma" role="UNKNOWN">γ</XMTok>
                    <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">J</XMTok>
                    <XMDual>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E47.m1.3"/>
                      <XMWrap>
                        <XMTok role="OPEN" stretchy="false">(</XMTok>
                        <XMTok font="italic" name="alpha" role="UNKNOWN" xml:id="S0.E47.m1.3">α</XMTok>
                        <XMTok role="CLOSE" stretchy="false">)</XMTok>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex87">
      <Math mode="display" tex="T_{0}+T_{0}^{\prime}=-{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}(\xi-\xi^{\prime})\cdot(Y_{0}-Y_{0}^%&#10;{\prime})\bigr{]}." text="T _ 0 + (T _ 0) ^ prime = - E * delimited-[]@((xi - xi ^ prime) cdot (Y _ 0 - (Y _ 0) ^ prime))" xml:id="S0.Ex87.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex87.m1.1"/>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex102">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle T_{1}^{i}&amp;\displaystyle={\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}(U^{i}_%&#10;{T}-{\bar{X}}^{i}_{T})\cdot\bar{Y}^{i}_{T}\bigr{]}+{\mathbb{E}}\biggl{[}\int_{%&#10;0}^{T}\bigl{(}f(s,U_{s}^{i},\bar{\nu}_{s}^{N},\beta_{s}^{i})-f(s,{\bar{X}}_{s}%&#10;^{i},\mu_{s},{\bar{\alpha}}_{s}^{i})\bigr{)}ds\biggr{]},\\&#10;\displaystyle T_{2}^{i}&amp;\displaystyle={\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}g(U^{i}_{T},\bar{\nu%&#10;}_{T}^{N})-g({\bar{X}}_{T}^{i},\mu_{T})\bigr{]}-{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}(U_{T}^{i}%&#10;-{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i})\cdot\partial_{x}g({\bar{X}}_{T}^{i},\mu_{T})\bigr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\phantom{??????????}-{\mathbb{E}}{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}(%&#10;{\tilde{}}U_{T}^{i}-{\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i})\cdot\partial_{\mu}g({\bar{X}}%&#10;_{T}^{i},\mu_{T})({\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i})\bigr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=T_{2,1}^{i}-T_{2,2}^{i}-T_{2,3}^{i},\end{split}" text="formulae@((T _ 1) ^ i = E * delimited-[]@(((U ^ i) _ T - ((bar@(X)) ^ i) _ T) cdot ((bar@(Y)) ^ i) _ T) + E * delimited-[]@(((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((f * vector@(s, (U _ s) ^ i, ((bar@(nu)) _ s) ^ N, (beta _ s) ^ i) - f * vector@(s, ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ i, mu _ s, ((bar@(alpha)) _ s) ^ i)) * differential-d@(s))), (T _ 2) ^ i = E * delimited-[]@(g * open-interval@((U ^ i) _ T, ((bar@(nu)) _ T) ^ N) - g * open-interval@(((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i, mu _ T)) - E * delimited-[]@((((U _ T) ^ i - ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i) cdot (partial-differential _ x)@(g)) * open-interval@(((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i, mu _ T)) - E * tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((tilde@(absent) * (U _ T) ^ i - tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i) cdot (partial-differential _ mu)@(g)) * open-interval@(((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i, mu _ T) * tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i) = (T _ (list@(2, 1))) ^ i - (T _ (list@(2, 2))) ^ i - (T _ (list@(2, 3))) ^ i)" xml:id="S0.Ex102.m1">

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex103">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle T_{2,3}^{i}&amp;\displaystyle={\mathbb{E}}{\tilde{}}{%&#10;\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}({\tilde{}}U_{T}^{i}-{\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i})\cdot%&#10;\partial_{\mu}g({\bar{X}}_{T}^{i},\mu_{T})({\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i})\bigr{]%&#10;}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=\frac{1}{N}\sum_{j=1}^{N}{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}({\tilde%&#10;{}}U_{T}^{i}-{\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i})\cdot\partial_{\mu}g({\tilde{}}{\bar{%&#10;X}}_{T}^{j},\mu_{T})({\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i})\bigr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 15.0pt+{\mathcal{O}}\biggl{(}{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{%&#10;[}|{\tilde{}}U_{T}^{i}-{\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i}|^{2}\bigr{]}^{1/2}{\tilde{}%&#10;}{\mathbb{E}}\biggl{[}\biggl{|}\frac{1}{N}\sum_{j=1}^{N}\partial_{\mu}g({%&#10;\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{j},\mu_{T})({\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i})-{\mathbb{E}}%&#10;\bigl{[}\partial_{\mu}g(\bar{X}_{T}^{i},\mu_{T})({\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i})%&#10;\bigr{]}\biggr{|}^{2}\biggr{]}^{1/2}\biggr{)}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=\frac{1}{N}\sum_{j=1}^{N}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}(U_{T}^{i}-{\bar{X%&#10;}}_{T}^{i})\cdot\partial_{\mu}g\bigl{(}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{j},\mu_{T})({\bar{X}}_{T%&#10;}^{i})\bigr{]}+{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|U_{T}^{i}-{\bar{X}}_{T}^{i}|^{2}\bigr{]}^{%&#10;1/2}{\mathcal{O}}(N^{-1/2}),\end{split}" text="(T _ (list@(2, 3))) ^ i = E * tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((tilde@(absent) * (U _ T) ^ i - tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i) cdot (partial-differential _ mu)@(g)) * open-interval@(((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i, mu _ T) * tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i) = (1 / N) * ((sum _ (j = 1)) ^ N)@(tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((tilde@(absent) * (U _ T) ^ i - tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i) cdot (partial-differential _ mu)@(g)) * open-interval@(tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ j, mu _ T) * tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i)) + O * tilde@(absent) * E * (delimited-[]@((absolute-value@(tilde@(absent) * (U _ T) ^ i - tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i)) ^ 2)) ^ (1 / 2) * tilde@(absent) * E * (delimited-[]@((absolute-value@((1 / N) * ((sum _ (j = 1)) ^ N)@((partial-differential _ mu)@(g) * open-interval@(tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ j, mu _ T) * tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i) - E * delimited-[]@((partial-differential _ mu)@(g) * open-interval@(((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i, mu _ T) * tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i))) ^ 2)) ^ (1 / 2) = (1 / N) * ((sum _ (j = 1)) ^ N)@(E * delimited-[]@((((U _ T) ^ i - ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i) cdot (partial-differential _ mu)@(g)) * open-interval@(((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ j, mu _ T) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i)) + E * (delimited-[]@((absolute-value@((U _ T) ^ i - ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ i)) ^ 2)) ^ (1 / 2) * O * N ^ (- 1 / 2)" xml:id="S0.Ex103.m1">

      <Math mode="display" tex="\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}T_{2,3}^{i}=\frac{1}{N}\sum_{j=1}^{N}{\mathbb{E}}%&#10;\tilde{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}(U_{T}^{\vartheta}-{\bar{X}}_{T}^{\vartheta})\cdot%&#10;\partial_{\mu}g\bigl{(}{\bar{X}}_{T}^{j},\mu_{T})({\bar{X}}_{T}^{\vartheta})%&#10;\bigr{]}+{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|U_{T}^{1}-{\bar{X}}_{T}^{1}|^{2}\bigr{]}^{1/2}{%&#10;\mathcal{O}}(N^{-1/2})." text="(1 / N) * ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@((T _ (list@(2, 3))) ^ i) = (1 / N) * ((sum _ (j = 1)) ^ N)@(E * tilde@(E) * delimited-[]@((((U _ T) ^ vartheta - ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ vartheta) cdot (partial-differential _ mu)@(g)) * open-interval@(((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ j, mu _ T) * ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ vartheta)) + E * (delimited-[]@((absolute-value@((U _ T) ^ 1 - ((bar@(X)) _ T) ^ 1)) ^ 2)) ^ (1 / 2) * O * N ^ (- 1 / 2)" xml:id="S0.Ex105.m1">

    <equation labels="LABEL:eq:30:1:2" xml:id="S0.E63">
      <tags>
        <tag>(63)</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">63</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}T_{1,3}^{i}&amp;\displaystyle=%&#10;\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}{\mathbb{E}}{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\biggl{[}\int_{0}^{%&#10;T}(U_{s}^{i}-{\bar{X}}_{s}^{i})\cdot\partial_{\mu}H(s,{\tilde{}}{\bar{X}}_{s}^%&#10;{i},\mu_{s},\tilde{\bar{Y}}_{s}^{i},\tilde{\bar{Z}}_{s}^{i},{\tilde{}}{\bar{%&#10;\alpha}}_{s}^{i})({\bar{X}}_{s}^{i})ds\biggr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=\frac{1}{N^{2}}\sum_{j=1}^{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}{\mathbb{E}}\biggl{[%&#10;}\int_{0}^{T}(U_{s}^{i}-{\bar{X}}_{s}^{i})\cdot\partial_{\mu}H(s,{\bar{X}}_{s}%&#10;^{j},\mu_{s},\bar{Y}_{s}^{j},\bar{Z}_{s}^{j},{\bar{\alpha}}_{s}^{j})({\bar{X}}%&#10;_{s}^{i})ds\biggr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 30.0pt+\biggl{(}{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}|U_{s}^{1}-{\bar{%&#10;X}}_{s}^{1}|^{2}ds\biggr{)}^{1/2}{\mathcal{O}}(N^{-1/2}).\end{split}" text="(1 / N) * ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@((T _ (list@(1, 3))) ^ i) = (1 / N) * ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@(E * tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((((U _ s) ^ i - ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ i) cdot (partial-differential _ mu)@(H)) * vector@(s, tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ i, mu _ s, ((tilde@(bar@(Y))) _ s) ^ i, ((tilde@(bar@(Z))) _ s) ^ i, tilde@(absent) * ((bar@(alpha)) _ s) ^ i) * ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ i * differential-d@(s)))) = (1 / N ^ 2) * ((sum _ (j = 1)) ^ N)@(((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@(E * delimited-[]@(((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((((U _ s) ^ i - ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ i) cdot (partial-differential _ mu)@(H)) * vector@(s, ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ j, mu _ s, ((bar@(Y)) _ s) ^ j, ((bar@(Z)) _ s) ^ j, ((bar@(alpha)) _ s) ^ j) * ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ i * differential-d@(s))))) + (E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((absolute-value@((U _ s) ^ 1 - ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ 1)) ^ 2 * differential-d@(s))) ^ (1 / 2) * O * N ^ (- 1 / 2)" xml:id="S0.E63.m1">

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex111">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}T_{1,3}^{i}&amp;\displaystyle=%&#10;\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}{\mathbb{E}}{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}\biggl{[}\int_{0}^{%&#10;T}(U_{s}^{\vartheta}-{\bar{X}}_{s}^{\vartheta})\cdot\partial_{\mu}H(s,{\bar{X}%&#10;}_{s}^{i},\mu_{s},\bar{Y}_{s}^{i},\bar{Z}_{s}^{i},{\bar{\alpha}}_{s}^{i})({%&#10;\bar{X}}_{s}^{\vartheta})ds\biggr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 30.0pt+\biggl{(}{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}|U_{s}^{1}-{\bar{%&#10;X}}_{s}^{1}|^{2}ds\biggr{)}^{1/2}{\mathcal{O}}(N^{-1/2})\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=\frac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N}{\mathbb{E}}{\tilde{}}{\mathbb{E}}%&#10;\biggl{[}\int_{0}^{T}(U_{s}^{\vartheta}-{\bar{X}}_{s}^{\vartheta})\cdot%&#10;\partial_{\mu}H(s,{\bar{X}}_{s}^{i},\bar{\mu}^{N}_{s},\bar{Y}_{s}^{i},\bar{Z}_%&#10;{s}^{i},{\bar{\alpha}}_{s}^{i})({\bar{X}}_{s}^{\vartheta})ds\biggr{]}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\hskip 30.0pt+\biggl{(}{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}|U_{s}^{1}-{\bar{%&#10;X}}_{s}^{1}|^{2}ds\biggr{)}^{1/2}{\mathcal{O}}(\ell_{N}(d)).\end{split}" text="(1 / N) * ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@((T _ (list@(1, 3))) ^ i) = (1 / N) * ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@(E * tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((((U _ s) ^ vartheta - ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ vartheta) cdot (partial-differential _ mu)@(H)) * vector@(s, ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ i, mu _ s, ((bar@(Y)) _ s) ^ i, ((bar@(Z)) _ s) ^ i, ((bar@(alpha)) _ s) ^ i) * ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ vartheta * differential-d@(s)))) + (E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((absolute-value@((U _ s) ^ 1 - ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ 1)) ^ 2 * differential-d@(s))) ^ (1 / 2) * O * N ^ (- 1 / 2) = (1 / N) * ((sum _ (i = 1)) ^ N)@(E * tilde@(absent) * E * delimited-[]@(((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((((U _ s) ^ vartheta - ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ vartheta) cdot (partial-differential _ mu)@(H)) * vector@(s, ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ i, ((bar@(mu)) ^ N) _ s, ((bar@(Y)) _ s) ^ i, ((bar@(Z)) _ s) ^ i, ((bar@(alpha)) _ s) ^ i) * ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ vartheta * differential-d@(s)))) + (E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((absolute-value@((U _ s) ^ 1 - ((bar@(X)) _ s) ^ 1)) ^ 2 * differential-d@(s))) ^ (1 / 2) * O * ell _ N * d" xml:id="S0.Ex111.m1">

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex115">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\sup_{0\leq t\leq T}{\mathbb{E}}\bigl{[}|U_{t}^{1}-{\bar{X}}_{t}^{1}|^{2}\bigr%&#10;{]}\leq C{\mathbb{E}}\int_{0}^{T}|\beta_{s}^{1}-{\bar{\alpha}}_{s}^{1}|^{2}ds," text="(supremum _ (0 less= t less= T))@(E * delimited-[]@((absolute-value@((U _ t) ^ 1 - ((bar@(X)) _ t) ^ 1)) ^ 2)) less= C * E * ((integral _ 0) ^ T)@((absolute-value@((beta _ s) ^ 1 - ((bar@(alpha)) _ s) ^ 1)) ^ 2 * differential-d@(s))" xml:id="S0.Ex115.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex115.m1.1"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex115.m1.1">
                <XMTok meaning="less-than-or-equals" name="leq" role="RELOP">≤</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMApp scriptpos="mid">
                    <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="mid2"/>
                    <XMTok meaning="supremum" role="LIMITOP" scriptpos="mid">sup</XMTok>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="multirelation"/>
                      <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="0" role="NUMBER">0</XMTok>

                      <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">t</XMTok>
                      <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="less-than-or-equals" name="leq" role="RELOP">≤</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">T</XMTok>
                    </XMApp>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
